    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><font color="red" size="5">1.引用 ThoughtWorks.QRCode.dll</font><p>NuGet包中搜索ThoughtWorks.QRCode进行安装</p><font color="red" size="5">2.简单二维码生成及解码代码</font><figure class="highlight csharp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">public</span> ActionResult <span class="title">CreateCode_Choose</span>(<span class="params"><span class="keyword">string</span> strData</span>)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>     &#123;</span><br><span class="line">         QRCodeEncoder qrCodeEncoder = <span class="keyword">new</span> QRCodeEncoder();</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//尺寸</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">string</span> encoding = <span class="string">"Byte"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">switch</span> (encoding)</span><br><span class="line">         &#123;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">"Byte"</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                 qrCodeEncoder.QRCodeEncodeMode = QRCodeEncoder.ENCODE_MODE.BYTE;</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">             <span class="keyword">default</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                 qrCodeEncoder.QRCodeEncodeMode = QRCodeEncoder.ENCODE_MODE.BYTE;</span><br><span class="line">                 <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         &#125;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//比例</span></span><br><span class="line">         qrCodeEncoder.QRCodeScale = <span class="number">4</span>;</span><br><span class="line">          <span class="comment">//版本</span></span><br><span class="line">         qrCodeEncoder.QRCodeVersion = <span class="number">8</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//大小</span></span><br><span class="line">         qrCodeEncoder.QRCodeErrorCorrect = QRCodeEncoder.ERROR_CORRECTION.L;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//文字生成图片</span></span><br><span class="line">         Image image = qrCodeEncoder.Encode(strData);</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">string</span> filename = DateTime.Now.ToString(<span class="string">"yyyymmddhhmmssfff"</span>).ToString() + <span class="string">".jpg"</span>;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">string</span> filepath = Server.MapPath(<span class="string">@"~\Images"</span>) + <span class="string">"\\"</span> + filename;</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//如果文件夹不存在，则创建</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//if (!Directory.Exists(filepath))</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="comment">//    Directory.CreateDirectory(filepath);</span></span><br><span class="line">         System.IO.FileStream fs = <span class="keyword">new</span> System.IO.FileStream(filepath, System.IO.FileMode.OpenOrCreate, System.IO.FileAccess.Write);</span><br><span class="line">         image.Save(fs, System.Drawing.Imaging.ImageFormat.Jpeg);</span><br><span class="line">         fs.Close();</span><br><span class="line">         image.Dispose();</span><br><span class="line">         <span class="keyword">return</span> Content(<span class="string">@"/Images/"</span> + filename);</span><br><span class="line">     &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><font color="red" size="5">3.前端进行调用</font><p>HTML展示<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;div&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;p&gt;路径：&lt;input id=&quot;strData&quot; type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;www.hackrost001.top&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;img src=&quot;&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; id=&quot;ewms&quot;/&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;input id=&quot;createCode&quot; type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;生成并保存在本地&quot; /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">    &lt;br /&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;/div&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>JQuery实现<br><figure class="highlight js"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$(<span class="built_in">document</span>).ready(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        $(<span class="string">"#createCode"</span>).click(<span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params"></span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">var</span> strData = $(<span class="string">"#strData"</span>).val();</span><br><span class="line">            $.post(<span class="string">"/home/CreateCode_Choose"</span>, &#123; <span class="attr">strData</span>: strData&#125;, <span class="function"><span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="params">data</span>) </span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">                $(<span class="string">"#ewms"</span>).attr(<span class="string">"src"</span>, data);</span><br><span class="line">            &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p>效果实现</p><p><img src="/2019/05/05/ThoughtWorks-QRCode/show.png" alt="avatar"></p>]]></content>
    
